title: Ukraine calls for cease-fire to evacuate civilians from Sievierodonetsk chemical plant | DW News
description: A Russian air strike killed four people in the eastern Ukrainian cities of Lysychansk, local residents said. The strike on a cultural center killed a mother and daughter, as well as a young man and a bedridden woman who had moved there to shelter from her home in Severodonetsk.|The bombing on Thursday sparked a fire that raged through Stalin-era Diamant Palace of Culture overnight and was still burning on Friday. Police said that around 10 people were injured, some seriously after being trapped by debris. Meanwhile, a key highway out of Lysychansk is now impassable due to Russian shelling, Luhansk regional governor Serhiy Gaidai said in an online post on Friday.|Serhiy Haidai, the governor of the eastern Ukrainian region of Luhansk, said that there are 568 people sheltering in the Azot chemical plant in the city of Sievierodonetsk, where fighting has been raging. "Exit from the plant is possible only with a complete cease-fire."|German Chancellor Olaf  Scholz has insisted that German weapons will arrive in time to help Ukraine fend off Russian forces in the eastern Donbas region. His comments, in an exclusive interview with DPA news agency, come amid criticism from Kyiv over the pace of weapons deliveries and the type of weapons sent.|Asked whether the heavy weaponry will arrive in time to make a difference in the Donbas, Scholz answered: "It will arrive in time." He said the priority for who gets German weapons first had to be changed as German arms manufacturers have a "long list of customers" waiting for deliveries. The chancellor promised to deliver an anti-ballistic missile system that is able to protect Odesa or Kyiv and said Berlin had decided together with the UK and the United States that it will deliver multiple rocket launchers.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|►Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|►Twitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|►Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|Für Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #EU

title: プーチン氏が演説「欧米による経済制裁は失敗した」(2022年6月18日)
description: ロシアのプーチン大統領が演説を行い、「欧米による経済制裁は失敗した」などと主張し、ウクライナを支援する欧米との対決姿勢を改めて強調しました。|　プーチン大統領：「冷戦後、アメリカは責任を負わず自分の利益のみを追求する神の使者だと宣言した」|　プーチン大統領は17日、経済フォーラムで演説し、エネルギー価格の高騰をはじめとする世界経済の悪化は欧米のせいだと述べ、ウクライナでの軍事作戦とは全く関係がないと主張しました。|　一方で、欧米による金融制裁は失敗し、ロシアの財政は安定していると強調し、制裁の打撃を受けているのはむしろ欧米側だと述べました。|　また、ウクライナでの軍事作戦を巡っては「すべての目的を達成するまで続ける」と改めて強調しています。|[テレ朝ｎｅｗｓ] https://news.tv-asahi.co.jp

title: heute journal vom 17.06.2022
description: Trotz beispielloser westlicher Sanktionen gegen Russland sieht Kremlchef Wladimir Putin die Rohstoffgroßmacht auf einem Erfolgskurs. Die Versuche, die russische Wirtschaft zu schwächen, seien gescheitert, sagte Putin auf dem Internationalen Wirtschaftsforum in St. Petersburg. Die wirtschaftlichen Sanktionen gegen Russland hätten keine Chance auf Erfolg. Mehr dazu und weitere Nachrichten des Tages im heute journal.|00:00 Vorspann|00:21 Sorgen um die Gasversorgung |Nicht nur Deutschland bekommt weniger Gas aus Russland, inzwischen sind mehrere europäische Länder betroffen. In Berlin sucht man nach sicheren Perspektiven für Deutschlands Gasversorgung.|05:03 Netzagentur-Chef: "Angespannte" Gas-Situation|Deutschland sei immer noch abhängig von russischen Gasimporten, sagt der Chef der Bundesnetzagentur Klaus Müller. Sinkende Liefermengen sorgten für eine "angespannte Situation". Müller appelliert an Verbraucher*innen und Industrie, Gas einzusparen.|11:41 AfD ermöglicht Einzelspitze|Im sächsischen Riesa hat der Parteitag der AfD begonnen. Die Delegierten stimmten dafür, künftig auch eine Einzelspitze zu ermöglichen. Nach den letzten Wahlniederlagen stehen die AfD und ihr Parteivorsitzender Chrupalla unter Druck.|17:27 Lauterbach: "Kein Alarm notwendig"|Die Infektionszahlen steigen wieder an, es gebe jedoch keinen Grund für Alarm, so Gesundheitsminister Lauterbach. Für den Herbst kündigt er ein neues Testkonzept sowie eine Impfkampagne an. Zudem will er ein verändertes Infektionsschutzgesetz vorlegen.|----- |Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen für Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erklären die Hintergründe und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet euch eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir euch präsentieren. |Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen. |Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf https://ZDFheute.de. |#Putin #Sanktionen #heutejournal

title: Bodycam Video Shows LAPD SWAT Shoot Alleged Armed Suspect During Standoff
description: The Los Angeles Police Department released bodycam video showing their SWAT team shooting an allegedly armed suspect, 54-year-old Leron James, on May 3. Central Patrol officers responded to a backup request from the Los Angeles Fire Department about a suicidal man. Upon arrival, the man pointed a gun at officers after they tried to speak to him, prompting officers to request additional backup from the LAPD SWAT team and the Crisis Negotiation team. The SWAT team used a chemical agent in an attempt to coerce the suspect out of his apartment. The suspect responded by shooting his firearm out his window, at which time an officer shot him. Officers pronounced the suspect deceased at the scene. title: Tiggo 8 Pro, 7 Pro, 5X, Arrizo 6 Pro e iCar - Novos CAOA Chery híbridos - Preço, detalhes, bom?
description: A CAOA Chery apresentou nessa semana 5 modelos de carros eletrificados que fazem parte da nova ofensiva da empresa focada em sustentabilidade e tecnologia. Os carros somente a combustão continuam à venda, mas os consumidores terão opções de modelos híbridos agora.|São três veículos Híbridos Leves, um modelo Híbrido Plug-in e um modelo 100% Elétrico e totalmente novo no mercado. E esse último é chamado iCar, um carro diminuto e urbano, com carroceria em alumínio e polímero que chega para ser o elétrico mais barato do Brasil (posto até entrão ocupado pelo Renault e-Kwid). Tem 61cv e 282km de autonomia e muito recursos, como multimídia, bancos elétricos e teto panorâmico.|Já o Híbrido Plug-in é o Tiggo 8 Pro Hybrid, que vem remodelado e chega com um motor 1.5 turbo aliado a uma transmissão de 11 velocidades e 2 motores elétricos que, combinados, entregam 317cv e 56,5kgfm de torque. Como tem bastante capacidade de bateria, pode rodar até 77km em modo elétrico e é o primeiro carro da CAOA a receber o sistema ADAS de segurança ativa, com frenagem autônoma, correção de faixa, farol alto adaptativo e ACC. E chega com valores bem abaixo de seus concorrentes, como Jeep Compass 4XE, mesmo tendo 7 lugares.|E os modelos de Híbridos Leves recebem a mesma motorização e câmbio, um motor 1.5 turbo flex com câmbio CVT e um sistema elétrico que adiciona 10cv e reduz o consumo. Além disso, Arrizo 6 Pro e Tiggo 5x Pro também receberam novos equipamentos. Já o Tiggo 7 Pro recebeu novas rodas e um design um pouco diferente. Todos são um pouco mais caros que as versões a combustão, mas bem competitivos no mercado.|No evento de lançamento pudemos conhecer os carros e mostrar um overview para vocês de tudo o que eles entregam. Contem para nós o que acharam dessas novidades, dos equipamentos, dos preços e tudo mais!|Abaixo tem link para vídeo de avaliação das versões somente a combustão desses modelos.|Vídeo sobre CAOA Chery Tiggo 8: https://youtu.be/in97KH-suyc|Vídeo sobre CAOA Chery Tiggo 7 Pro: https://youtu.be/uvrpQ9tR_TA|Vídeo sobre CAOA Chery Tiggo 5x: https://youtu.be/FcmDO72FHO0|Vídeo sobre CAOA Chery Arrizo 6 Pro: https://youtu.be/WGHsd9TEf8s|Parceiros (links no primeiro comentário):|Olho no Carro|Virgola|Klaue Corretora de Seguros|Carro Favorito|Tuio Car Detail|KBB Brasil|PneuStore|SuperBike Store|Torne-se Membro e tenha acesso a conteúdos exclusivos: |https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCc0cU92Tf7rvd2gr-CpVO4Q/join|Nos siga:|Instagram: @op.sincera|TikTok: @op.sincera |Facebook: fb.com/op.sincera|YouTube: youtube.com/opiniaosincera|Entre em contato: |Parcerias: opiniaosincera@sousagaz.com.br|Dúvidas: canalopiniaosincera@gmail.com|#opiniaosincera #caoachery #eletrificados

title: 「ロシアに対する経済電撃戦は失敗」プーチン氏 国際経済会議で演説｜TBS NEWS DIG
description: ロシアのプーチン大統領が国際経済会議で演説し、欧米の制裁について「ロシアに対する経済電撃戦は失敗した」と主張しました。|ロシア プーチン大統領|「ロシアに対する経済電撃戦は成功しなかった」|プーチン氏は17日、ロシアの「サンクトペテルブルク国際経済フォーラム」で演説し、欧米が制裁によってロシア経済を崩壊させようとする試みは失敗したと主張。制裁はむしろ欧米の経済に打撃を与えていると語りました。|ロシア プーチン大統領|「反ロシア制裁によるEUの直接的な損失は、この1年で4000億ドル以上に達する可能性がある」|また、食糧危機やエネルギーの問題は欧米の誤った経済政策によるもので「ウクライナでの特別軍事作戦は何の関係もない」と強調しました。|会議では中国の習近平国家主席も事前に撮影したビデオ演説で、「一方的な制裁や極端な圧力を放棄し、世界経済の回復を達成すべきだ」と主張しました。|一方、この日、EU委員会はEU加盟を申請していたウクライナについて、交渉開始の前提となる「加盟候補国」に認めるよう加盟国に勧告したことを明らかにしました。候補国に認められるにはすべての加盟国の同意が必要で来週のEU首脳会議で議論される見通しです。|▼TBS NEWS DIG 公式サイト　https://newsdig.tbs.co.jp/|▼チャンネル登録をお願いします！|http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6AG81pAkf6Lbi_1VC5NmPA?sub_confirmation=1|▼情報提供はこちらから「TBSインサイダーズ」|https://www.tbs.co.jp/news_sp/tbs-insiders.html|▼映像提供はこちらから「TBSスクープ投稿」|https://www.tbs.co.jp/news_sp/toukou.html

Adamın biri yanlarına gelerek Tunç'u vurur ve arabasının bagajına atarak oradan uzaklaşır. Tunç'un sevgilisi hemen Mesut'a haber verir. Araba herkesin gözleri önünde uçurumdan aşağı yuvarlanır ve infilak eder. title: Çoban Evinde Sorgu Zamanı! | Arka Sokaklar 632. Bölüm SEZON FİNALİ
description: Çoban Evinde Sorgu Zamanı! | Arka Sokaklar 632. Bölüm SEZON FİNALİ|Efsane dizi 16. Sezon finaliyle ekrana geliyor. İlyas'ın silah doğrulttuğu Pınar'ın yaşayıp, yaşamadığı merak konusu oluyor. Rıza Baba ve eşi Ayla, hastanede acı için bekleyişlerini sürdürüyor. Ekip ise, Caner ve dayısı İlyas'ın peşine düşüyor.|Yüzyıllara meydan okuyan, büyülü, kocaman bir şehir ; İstanbul. Ve bu şehrin her sokağını, herkes için daha güzel, daha ‘yaşanır’ bir yer yapmak uğruna her türlü kötülüğe ve sıkıntıya meydan okuyan yürekli polislerimiz…|İstanbul Polis Teşkilatı Asayiş Şube’de görev yapan ‘sivil’ bir ekip, minibüsleriyle bu metropolün sokaklarını arşınlamakta ve karşılarına çıkan her türlü kanunsuzlukla savaşmaktadırlar. title: Senden Daha Güzel 3. Bölüm 2. Fragmanı @Senden Daha Güzel
description: Senden Daha Güzel 3. Bölüm 2. Fragmanı |Dermatolog olarak çalışan Efsun, Gaziantep’te bir köyde babasıyla birlikte  çiftlikte  huzur içinde yaşamaktadır. Annesi küçük yaşta onu ve babasını terk ederek İstanbul’a taşınmış ve Türkiye’nin en önemli estetik cerrahlarından biri olmuştur. Efsun‘a 12 yaşından bu yana görüşmediği annesinden bir anda haber gelir. Annesi ölüm döşeğindedir ve onunla son bir kez görüşmek istemektedir. Şoförünü göndererek Efsun’u İstanbul’a davet eder. Annesini görmek için İstanbul’a giden Efsun büyük bir sürprizle karşılaşır. İstanbul’un en büyük estetik kliniğinin sahibi olan annesi, Efsun’dan klinikte çalışmasını ister ve bunun için onu zorlar. Bütün bunlar yetmiyor gibi, şoför sandığı Emir aslında annesinin ortağı Kaya Bey’in oğludur. Yakışıklı, karizmatik bir cerrah olan Emir, Efsun’un kliniği elinden almaya geldiğini sanıp Efsun ile mücadeleye girişir. title: Vincent Biruta : "Le Rwanda veut une désescalade pour ne pas entrer en guerre avec la RD Congo"
description: Vincent Biruta, ministre rwandais des Affaires étrangères, évoque les tensions qui s'aggravent entre son pays et le voisin congolais. Il confirme qu'un soldat de la RD Congo a été tué, vendredi 17 juin, après être entré au Rwanda et avoir blessé des policiers rwandais. Des manifestations organisées cette semaine à Goma ont entraîné la fermeture des frontières et la rupture de traités liant les deux pays. title: Starship Troopers: Terran Command Review
description: Starship Troopers: Terran Command reviewed by Leana Hafer on PC.||||Starship Troopers: Terran Command has the exoskeleton of a strong RTS with some unique, asymmetrical, positioning-focused warfare. There are just a handful of hitches that keep it from being really great. A campaign that takes too long to become challenging, some frustratingly bad pathfinding and targeting AI, and the lack of multiplayer or a scenario editor are the main ones. But if all you're looking for is a competent single-player campaign that hits all the notes I'd expect as a Starship Troopers fan, and eventually provides some diverse and challenging tactical puzzles to solve, you'll find it here.|#IGN #Gaming

title: Menggembirakan, Indonesia Memiliki Tingkat Produktivitas Gabah ke 2 di Asia Tenggara
description: KOMPAS.TV - Produksi pertanian di tahun 2020 dan 2021, mencatatkan pertumbuhan yang positif, ialah produksi padi di tanah air.||||Indonesia memang dikenal sebagai negara dengan angka konsumsi beras tertinggi di dunia, atau setara 97,6 kilogram perkapita.||||Dalam neraca tahunan 2020-2021, Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS) mencatat peningkatan produksi hingga serapan di konsumen.||||Diantara negara Asia pun, Indonesia menjadi negara kedua yang memiliki tingkat produktivitas gabah tertinggi.||||Baca Juga Motor Hangus Terbakar di Jalan Raya Serpong Usai Tabrak Pejalan Kaki di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300268/motor-hangus-terbakar-di-jalan-raya-serpong-usai-tabrak-pejalan-kaki||||Diposisi pertama terdapat Vietnam, dengan perkiraan produksi 5,82 juta ton perhektar.||||Berbanding lurus dengan produksi gabah yang tinggi, melimpahnya padi di tanah air membuat harga jual beras pun ikut bersaing, tak heran diantara 11 negara Asean, Indonesia ternyata menjadi negara kedua yang memiliki harga beras termurah.||||Selama lebih dari setahun di 2020, Bulog mencatatkan 511 ribu ton stok buang.||||Stok buang yang dimaksud cadangan beras yang mutunya atau title: The Callisto Protocol Reveal Destroys IGN’s Summer of Gaming 2022
description: The Callisto Protocol invaded IGN's Summer of Gaming and it definitely was not a safe place for anyone here in the studio, and all the chaos was sponsored by The Callisto Protocol.||||The Callisto Protocol is a a third-person sci-fi horror survival  game developed by Striking Distance Studios and was founded by Dead Space creator Glen Schofield. ||You play as Jacob Lee, voiced by Josh Duhamel, who is a prisoner on the moon trying to survive during a "mysterious outbreak" that's mutating people into terrible monsters called Biophage. Schofield says "horror starts with atmosphere," and that special antention has been paid to things like lighting and the PS5's 3D audio. The Callisto Protocol will also take advantage of The Dualsense controller's haptics for everything from heavy enemy footsteps to swinging your weapon. ||||The Callisto Protocol realease December 2, 2022 on Xbox One, Playstation 4, Playstation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.|#IGN #IGNSummerOfGaming

title: VISITING DDE HQ! Damon's Porsche Carrera GT MAKEOVER in Signal Green
description: It's 'Signal Green' Porsche Carrera GT time! @DailyDrivenExotics have remodelled their HQ in LA, and now given the CGT a new look too. Let's check it out at PFS before heading over to the garage to check out what's going on. That V10 is a masterpiece, and who needs tires anyway...|Damon bought the iconic Porsche supercar a year ago, originally in Seal Grey over Terracotta, but has now taken it to @Protective Film Solutions for an all new look in a wrap like Porsche's PTS Signal Green. After meeting up and taking a look at the changes including the new AL13 wheels and gloss black elements around the car, it's time for a catch up and drive out on the road to head to DDE HQ.|It wasn't that long ago that Damon and Dave got the keys to their shop, although while they've been away on @Gumball 3000, the whole place has had an extensive remodelling; from the floor to walls and the new lighting that's just been installed. At the moment it features 3 generations of Lamborghini V12; Aventador SVJ, Murcielago LP640 and Diablo SV, plus the Ferrari 550 Maranello project build, and a few of the Viper drift cars amongst others.|Inspired by Fast and the Furious, the DDE HQ features a storage area, working area, team kitchen and offices, and will be home to many of their ongoing projects. Oh, and there turn out to be some fairly random items around too... title: WATCH: Why Mike Pence refused to leave the Capitol on Jan. 6 #shorts
description: During the Jan. 6 committee hearing on June 16, Greg Jacob, the chief counsel to former Vice President Mike Pence, said Pence refused to leave the U.S. Capitol as rioters breached the building on Jan. 6, 2021.|Pence had been moved to a secured location as rioters moved through the building. At one point, the head of his Secret Service detail asked him to get into a car for his safety. Pence refused, saying he did not want to risk the car leaving with him in it.| "The vice president did not want to take any chance that the world would see the vice president of the United States, fleeing the United States Capitol," Jacob said.|Jacob added that Pence was "determined" to certify the votes and did not want to give the rioters the "satisfaction" of further delaying or stopping the count.|The committee presented new evidence about the danger Pence faced  as former President Donald Trump sent out a tweet criticizing the vice president. As rioters at the Capitol focused their anger on the vice president, they at one point came within 40 feet of Pence within the building.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@pbsnews|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe:|PBS NewsHour podcasts: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/podcasts|Newsletters: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/subscribe

title: Pink Panther Finds a Magic Wand | 35 Minute Compilation | Pink Panther Show
description: 1. Pinto Pink - A weary, footsore Pink Panther is trying to thumb a ride to Los Angeles when a smart-aleck horse catches his eye, and he decides to ride the poor beast into town. However, the ornery beast has ideas of his own.|2. Pink Tuba-Dore - A tuba player arrives in the forest with his dog to play his tuba in peace, unaware that the Pink Panther is sleeping and he is disrupting him greatly. |3. Pink-A-Rella - When the Pink Panther finds a magic wand in a poor neighborhood, he sets about beautifying the area. description: Plan de apoyo a la población afectada por el huracán Agatha, desde Oaxaca. Viernes 17 de junio 2022 | Presidente AMLO. |En Huatulco, nos reunimos con integrantes del Gabinete y autoridades locales para dar seguimiento al Plan de apoyo a la población de Oaxaca afectada por el huracán Agatha. |Hoy inicia la entrega de enseres domésticos y el lunes 20 de junio la de recursos a familias damnificadas y productores. Se realizará de manera directa, con base en el Censo del Bienestar. |Los paquetes de insumos para el hogar contienen un refrigerador, una estufa, una licuadora, un ventilador, un colchón y un juego de sartenes. |Está en marcha la rehabilitación de escuelas, unidades médicas, caminos y puentes de los 31 municipios afectados con una inversión de mil 800 millones de pesos; el gobierno estatal aportará el 30 por ciento de ese monto. |Al final de este año, Oaxaca tendrá un sistema de salud digno y de calidad a través del sistema IMSS Bienestar, programa para garantizar el acceso a servicios médicos gratuitos a la población sin seguridad social.|El 17 de septiembre regresaremos a evaluar resultados. Concubia acestuia tocmai născuse o fetiță, iar bărbatul nu a mai venit să le ia acasă din spital. O lună mai târziu un cioban găsește un craniu pe un deal aflat într-un loc izolat la marginea comunei. Un an mai târziu un copil de 5 ani povestește la grădiniță faptul că tatăl său a omorât un bărbat, iar cu părți din corpul acestuia a hrănit câinele familiei. Șocate, educatoarele au sesizat poliția. title: L'appel du 18 juin | Film complet en français
description: Le 17 juin 1940, en pleine débâcle des armées françaises, Charles De Gaulle, un obscur Général de brigade promu depuis le 6 juin Sous Secrétaire d'État à la Guerre, est reçu par Churchill et apprend que le Maréchal Pétain vient d'appeler à cesser le combat et de demander à Hitler les conditions d'un armistice. De Gaulle exprime au Premier ministre anglais son désir de parler à la BBC, Churchill l'y autorise. Le lendemain du 18 juin à 22 heures, le général lance son appel à la résistance.|Réalisateur : Félix Olivier|Par Laurent : Herbiet, Philippe Madral|Avec Michel Vuillermoz, Clément Roussier, Christian Rodska|Production : Boreales

title: Çoban, Alper'i Havada Salladı! | Arka Sokaklar 632. Bölüm SEZON FİNALİ
description: Çoban, Alper'i Havada Salladı! | Arka Sokaklar 632. Bölüm SEZON FİNALİ|Efsane dizi 16. Sezon finaliyle ekrana geliyor. İlyas'ın silah doğrulttuğu Pınar'ın yaşayıp, yaşamadığı merak konusu oluyor. Rıza Baba ve eşi Ayla, hastanede acı için bekleyişlerini sürdürüyor. Ekip ise, Caner ve dayısı İlyas'ın peşine düşüyor.|Yüzyıllara meydan okuyan, büyülü, kocaman bir şehir ; İstanbul. Ve bu şehrin her sokağını, herkes için daha güzel, daha ‘yaşanır’ bir yer yapmak uğruna her türlü kötülüğe ve sıkıntıya meydan okuyan yürekli polislerimiz…|İstanbul Polis Teşkilatı Asayiş Şube’de görev yapan ‘sivil’ bir ekip, minibüsleriyle bu metropolün sokaklarını arşınlamakta ve karşılarına çıkan her türlü kanunsuzlukla savaşmaktadırlar. Polislerimiz, görevleri sırasında, değişik ve çeşitli insan hikayeleriyle sürekli karşılaşmaktadır. Zaman zaman gülümseten, zaman zaman da iç burkan bu hikayelere; meslek yıllarının tecrübesi ve ‘babalığıyla’ yaklaşan, ekibin diğer genç üyelerine de yol gösteren Rıza Baba olur. İlyas'ın silah doğrulttuğu Pınar'ın yaşayıp, yaşamadığı merak konusu oluyor. Rıza Baba ve eşi Ayla, hastanede acı için bekleyişlerini sürdürüyor. Ekip ise, Caner ve dayısı İlyas'ın peşine düşüyor.|Yüzyıllara meydan okuyan, büyülü, kocaman bir şehir ; İstanbul. title: Поховання для рашистів: українці залишаються людьми навіть з ворогами
description: Українці залишаються людьми навіть з ворогами. За 2 з половиною місяці відтоді, як російські війська відійшли з Київщини, окрім вбитих і зниклих безвісти наших земляків, пошуковці у тій частині області, яка була окупована, знаходять останки рашистів. Іноді - ці поховання тоді, у квітні, організовували самі ж місцеві люди, які пережили обстріли і тортури від окупантів. İlyas'ın silah doğrulttuğu Pınar'ın yaşayıp, yaşamadığı merak konusu oluyor. Rıza Baba ve eşi Ayla, hastanede acı için bekleyişlerini sürdürüyor. Ekip ise, Caner ve dayısı İlyas'ın peşine düşüyor.|Yüzyıllara meydan okuyan, büyülü, kocaman bir şehir ; İstanbul. Polislerimiz, görevleri sırasında, değişik ve çeşitli insan hikayeleriyle sürekli karşılaşmaktadır. Zaman zaman gülümseten, zaman zaman da iç burkan bu hikayelere; meslek yıllarının tecrübesi ve ‘babalığıyla’ yaklaşan, ekibin diğer genç üyelerine de yol gösteren Rıza Baba olur. Rıza Baba;  ekibe, hem mesleğe hem de hayata dair pek çok şeyi öğretecek, unutulanları hatırlatacaktır.|Kısacası, polislerimizin ve ailelerinin hayatları ile İstanbul sokaklarının serüveni iç içe geçecek, kahramanlarımız; sevinçte, kederde, aşkta ve yalnızlıkta her zaman birbirlerinin yanında olacaklar. title: How Stolen Goods End Up On Amazon, eBay And Facebook Marketplace
description: Coordinated robberies have hit dozens of U.S. stores in recent months and lawmakers are warning it’s a rising trend of organized retail crime. While punishments for shoplifters are hotly debated, there’s growing consensus around a solution that holds an entirely different group accountable: the online sites where the stolen goods are sold. Here’s what Amazon, eBay and Meta’s Facebook Marketplace say they’re already doing to stop the sale of stolen products on their platforms, and why major retailers like Home Depot are asking congress to crack down on them by requiring stricter verification of sellers.|Chapters:|00:00 -- Intro|01:55 -- Prevention and tracking|06:02 -- How stolen goods end up online|10:19 -- What eBay, Amazon and Meta do now|15:45 -- Legislation as a last resort|» Subscribe to CNBC: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|» Subscribe to CNBC TV: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCtelevision|» Subscribe to CNBC Classic: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCclassic|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: Chico Buarque | Que Tal Um Samba? feat Hamilton de Holanda (Lyric Vídeo)
description: Lyric Vídeo do novo single "Que Tal Um Samba?" de Chico Buarque feat Hamilton de Holanda.|Escute "Que Tal Um Samba?" na sua plataforma digital favorita: https://orcd.co/quetalumsamba|Inscreva-se no canal da Biscoito Fino!|Depois de alguns anos praticamente dedicados à literatura, que resultaram no romance ‘Essa gente’ e no volume de contos ‘Anos de chumbo’ - cujo título e histórias refletem o contexto desses anos de baixo astral, pandemia, abandono e tragédia política – os dedos largaram as teclas do computador e finalmente de volta ao instrumento pareciam mesmo se rebelar e a procurar uma batida diferente, feliz, quase eufórica, uma levada ao violão como a insistir: ‘Que tal um samba?’. |E aí, levada de samba nos dedos, cabeça e coração voltaram a pensar e a sentir a música e a agir. E Chico Buarque, como é bem de seu feitio, começou a recordar velhos sambas, um especialmente, sucesso de Blecaute no carnaval feliz de 1949, ‘Que samba bom’, composição de Geraldo Pereira também numa levada toda sincopada como a sua, algo eufórica, “ô, que samba bom/ô, que coisa louca/eu também tô aí/tô aí, que é que há/também tô nessa boca...”. Sambas sobre samba, o ‘Feitio de oração’ de Vadico e Noel Rosa, essa tradição e esse espírito vinham junto com a levada ao violão como a propor ao compositor enferrujado: ‘Que tal um samba?’.|E aí, da levada criada exclusivamente pelos dedos se exercitando ao violão, o coração e a cabeça fizeram brotar uma melodia espontânea, fluente, a harmonia como sempre personalíssima. A letra, depois de alguns caminhos abandonados, veio aos borbotões. Um samba novo enfim, diferente de todos os outros que já fez, mas no mesmo espírito que baixa sempre quando o compositor de ‘Tem mais samba’, de ‘Apesar de você’, de ‘Vai passar’, de ‘De volta ao samba’ parece ter algo importante a notar e a dizer. Como sempre, nessas ocasiões importantes, em forma de samba.|QUE TAL UM SAMBA?|Um samba|Que tal um samba?|Puxar um samba, que tal?|Para espantar o tempo feio|Para remediar o estrago|Que tal um trago?|Um desafogo, um devaneio| |Um samba pra alegrar o dia |Pra zerar o jogo|Coração pegando fogo  |E cabeça fria|Um samba com categoria, com calma| |Cair no mar, lavar a alma|Tomar um banho de sal grosso, que tal?|Sair do fundo do poço|Andar de boa|Ver um batuque lá no cais do Valongo |Dançar o jongo lá na Pedra do Sal|Entrar na roda da Gamboa| |Fazer um gol de bicicleta|Dar de goleada|Deitar na cama da amada|Despertar poeta|Achar a rima que completa o estribilho| |Fazer um filho, que tal?|Pra ver crescer, criar um filho|Num bom lugar, numa cidade legal|Um filho com a pele escura |Com formosura|Bem brasileiro, que tal?|Não com dinheiro|Mas a cultura| |Que tal uma beleza pura|No fim da borrasca?|Já depois de criar casca  |E perder a ternura|Depois de muita bola fora da meta| |De novo com a coluna ereta, que tal?|Juntar os cacos, ir à luta|Manter o rumo e a cadência|Esconjurar a ignorância, que tal?|Desmantelar a força bruta|Então que tal puxar um samba|Puxar um samba legal|Puxar um samba porreta|Depois de tanta mutreta|Depois de tanta cascata|Depois de tanta derrota|Depois de tanta demência|E de uma dor filha da puta, que tal?|Puxar um samba|Que tal um samba?|Um samba|#ChicoBuarque #QueTalUmSamba #MPB

title: «Vous imaginez, toute la journée devant la broche ?» : des kébabiers face à la canicule
description: « Ça fait un hammam gratuit… C’est trop chaud », plaisante Mehmet, exposé à la fournaise d’une brochette de viande en pleine cuisson. Entre l’huile de la friteuse en ébullition et les grilles métalliques chauffées à blanc de la machine à kebab , la température s’élève à 45-50°C dans le coin cuisine, estime le gérant de l’établissement. « Quand il n’y a pas beaucoup de monde, on baisse le feu », explique le cinquantenaire en diminuant la cuisson de la broche. L’exposition à la chaleur, c’est son quotidien. Mais avec la canicule qui s’abat actuellement sur la France, la tâche devient plus compliquée et la fenêtre ouverte de sa cuisine ne laisse plus pénétrer l’air frais. « Je suis habitué à la chaleur. Et je sais que ça va durer seulement quelques jours », relativise Mehmet. Au-delà du confort, la canicule impacte ses livraisons. « On reçoit les frites tous les jours. On ne peut pas les stocker avec cette chaleur », détaille-t-il. Reportage à voir dans la vidéo en tête d’article.

title: Does Steph Curry belong in the Top 10 All-Time after winning Finals MVP? | NBA | UNDISPUTED

title: 192 Kepala Daerah dari PDI-P Ikuti Sekolah Partai, Ganjar Hadir Usai Disebut Kemlinthi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Ratusan kepala daerah yang merupakan kader PDI Perjuangan, berolahraga bersama pada hari terakhir sekolah partai di Lenteng Agung, Jakarta Selatan.||||Tampak di antara kepala daerah yang mengikuti senam bersama, Wali Kota Solo Gibran Rakabuming Raka, Wali Kota Medan yang juga ipar Gibran, Bobby Nasution, dan Gubernur Jawa Tengah, Ganjar Pranowo. selain itu tampak pula Sekjen PDI Perjuangan, Hasto Kristiyanto.||||Kemunculan Ganjar Pranowo dalam acara sekolah partai di Lenteng Agung, mengundang perhatian. ||||Sebab belakangan sejumlah politisi PDIP kerap mengritik Ganjar yang dianggap terlalu berambisi maju dalam Pilpres 2024. ||||Baca Juga Partai Nasdem Usulkan 3 Nama Capres, Anies dan Ganjar Paling Banyak Dipilih di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300203/partai-nasdem-usulkan-3-nama-capres-anies-dan-ganjar-paling-banyak-dipilih||||Dalam unggahan di akun instagramnya, Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo menunjukkan bangsal yang ia tinggali, selama mengikuti sekolah partai bersama para kepala daerah dari PDI Perjuangan.||||Mess tempat Ganjar menginap, berisi sejumlah tempat tidur bertingkat dan lemari kecil. ||||Selama acara berlangsung, para kepala daerah menginap bersama tanpa didampingi ajudan masing-masing.||||192 kepala daerah dari PDI - Perjuangan, mengikuti rapat konsolidasi kepala daerah di sekolah partai selama dua hari, yang berakhir hari ini.||||Rapat koordinasi ini diadakan sebagai persiapan menghadapi pemilu 2024. ||||Para kepala daerah mendapatkan sejumlah pembekalan, salah satunya dari Menteri Keuangan Sri Mulyani.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300228/192-kepala-daerah-dari-pdi-p-ikuti-sekolah-partai-ganjar-hadir-usai-disebut-kemlinthi

title: Putin: "Wirtschaftlicher Blitzkrieg" des Westens gescheitert

title: Nupur Sharma missing? Mumbai cops hunt for 'untraceable' suspended BJP leader over Prophet row
description: Former BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma, who sparked fury in India and among Islamic nations with her remarks on the Prophet, is missing. Mumbai police have said that she is untraceable for 4 days now. This comes just 8 days ahead of her appearance before Mumbai police, to record a statement in connection to a FIR filed against her. The case was filed on May 29 following a complaint by Irfan Shaikh, the joint secretary of Mumbai wing of Raza Academy. Nupur Sharma was booked on charges of hurting religious feelings, promoting enmity and causing public mischief. title: 「書店は街に必要？」赤坂・文教堂が閉店　書店減少のなか“偏愛”テーマの“新たな書店”の形も｜TBS NEWS DIG
description: 東京・赤坂駅周辺で最後の1軒だった一般書店が閉店しました。街から書店が減り続ける一方、“新しい書店の形”が注目されています。|■「書店は街に必要か」　“出会い”を大切にしてきた書店が閉店　|6月17日夜、27年間の営業に幕を閉じた「文教堂　赤坂店」。周辺エリアの再開発計画に伴い、閉店となりました。|利用客（30代）|「やっぱりさみしいですね。たまにふらっときて店内うろついて『こんな本出ているんだ』と衝動的に買ったりとか、それも紙の本屋さんの良さかなと思う」|利用客（30代）|「会社に入ってすぐの時に会社関係の本を買いに来て、そこで頑張ろうかなと思った思い出がある」|赤坂駅周辺には一般書店が3軒ありましたが、この1年程で全て閉店に。|手作りのポスターには「赤坂駅周辺の書店が無くなる…」というタイトルで、こんな文言が綴られていました。|ポスターの文言|「本屋が無くなってしまいます。書店という業態は世の中に街に必要とされなくなっているのだろうか?」|どんな思いでこれを書いたのか、本人に聞きました。|文教堂　エリアマネージャー　富田利之さん|「仲間と話している思いが、そのままにじみ出てしまったのかもしれません。やはりお店がなくなって辞めていったスタッフや仲間もいますし、業界を去っていった友達もいますし」|書店が無くなるさみしさを素直に綴ると、利用客からの書き込みが…|「No BookStore！ No Life！！」|「また帰ってきて下さい。待っています…！」|閉店を惜しむ声。ここには街の書店ならではの“出会い”があるとスタッフはいいます。|「文教堂」赤坂店　コミック担当者|「なるべく新しい出会いがあるように他ではみられないような、でも面白いものを揃えたいと」|本棚を作るときも、「本との出会い」を大切にしてきたのです。|利用客の少年（12）|「ここにはたくさん感謝の気持ちがある。店員さんと話していく中で、買うときも心がこもっている。ネットだったら、ぽちっとマウス押せば買えるので（書店は）心の人と人のつながりがすごいかなと思う」|■”誰でも本屋になれる”　自分の情熱を伝える新しい書店|書店は減り続けています。全国で2万店以上あったものが、この20年で半減。単純計算で、1年に500店舗ちかくなくなっていることになります。|そんな中、新しい書店の形を作り出す動きも。|東京・渋谷のヒカリエに入っている「渋谷〇〇（まるまる）書店」。店内に並べられているのは130個の本棚。その1つ1つに違う書店の名前がついています。|「渋谷〇〇書店」管理人　横石崇さん|「渋谷シルクロード書店さんですね。シルクロード愛をもって本を集められていて、その一部をここに出したいということで」|「渋谷ARMY書店」は、BTS関連の書籍を販売する店。|「渋谷にゃんこ＆きゅん♡書店」では猫と、羽生結弦選手関連の本が集まっています。|「渋谷〇〇書店」管理人　横石崇さん|「偏愛をテーマにしているので、偏った愛、情熱を傾けられるものですね」|ここは個人に棚を貸し出し、それぞれが好きな本を持ち寄り販売する”シェア型書店”。本棚の賃料は月4950円。新品でも古本でも自費出版の本でも、自分の好きなものを好きな価格で販売できます。|生態学に関する本を並べている「水たまり書店」。店長の女性は、自分が学んできたことを|誰かに伝えたくて本を売るのだといいます。|渋谷「水たまり書店」店長|「学んできたことをいきなり講演会とかできるかというとそこまでの力もなくて、こういうスタイルだったら伝えたいことを本という形で並べて何かできるんじゃないかなと」|たまに売れると、誰が買ったのか不思議に思う一方で…|渋谷「水たまり書店」店長|「伝えたいことが入っている本を置いているので、それを誰かが読んでくださっているというのがとてもうれしいと感じる」|お客さんの評判も上々です。|利用客（20代）|「1人の人とか1人の書店が好きなコアなものって、本当にいいものっぽいなって個人的には感じるので、すごく惹かれますね」|「渋谷〇〇書店」管理人　横石崇さん|「この本屋さんというのは『つながる』、本とつながる、本でつながる、人とつながるという感覚がある場所だと思っているんで、それは今まで『書店』と言われているところと違うところなのかなと思う」|▼TBS NEWS DIG 公式サイト　https://newsdig.tbs.co.jp/|▼チャンネル登録をお願いします！|http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6AG81pAkf6Lbi_1VC5NmPA?sub_confirmation=1|▼情報提供はこちらから「TBSインサイダーズ」|https://www.tbs.co.jp/news_sp/tbs-insiders.html|▼映像提供はこちらから「TBSスクープ投稿」|https://www.tbs.co.jp/news_sp/toukou.html

title: ‘Riverdale’ Actor Pleads Guilty to Killing His Mom
description: A child star is facing serious allegations. Ryan Grantham, who appeared in the movie "Diary of a Wimpy Kid" and the hit TV series "Riverdale," pled guilty to killing his own mother in British Columbia, Canada. The actor also allegedly had plans to assassinate Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau. The day after allegedly murdering his mother, he loaded his car with three guns, ammunition, 12 Molotov cocktails and a map to where the prime minister and his family live.

title: 裏返しになったカメを救え　甲羅仲間かけつけ熱い絆
description: 兵庫・姫路市の動物園で、1匹のカメがひっくり返っている。|起き上がろうと必死に足を動かすが、なかなかうまくいかない。|そこへ近づいてきたのは、もう1匹のカメと、アルマジロ。|甲羅を持つ仲間としてアルマジロも助けに来たと思いきや、突然、後ろをうろうろと走りだす。|撮影者「普通にいたのに急に慌てて走りだしたので、『大変だ大変だ』っていう感じだったので、おもしろくて」|戻って来たと思えば、何もできずに、またうろうろ。|その一方で、仲間のカメは、背中を押し続けた。|そして、無事に起き上がることができた。|撮影した人によると、カメが2匹でじゃれていたところ、ひっくり返ってしまったという。|FNNプライムオンライン|https://www.fnn.jp/

title: 車2台が大破 運転手姿消す　0歳・1歳も...家族4人がけが
description: 車同士が衝突し、家族4人がけが。|片方の運転手が姿を消している。|交通量の多い道路で2台の大破した車が止まっている。|生後2カ月と1歳の子どもを含む4人がけがをする事故が発生した。|黒い車は横転し、フロントガラスが粉々に割れている。|もう1台の白い車は、ボンネットが折れ曲がるなど前の部分が激しく損傷。|事故が起きたのは17日午前10時半ごろ。|千葉・船橋市の信号のある交差点で、2台の車が衝突し、1台が横転した。|横転した黒い車に乗っていたのは、30代の父親と20代の母親、そして、生後2カ月と1歳の子どもの4人だった。|両親は自力で脱出し、その後、子ども2人は駆け付けた消防隊が救出。|4人は病院に搬送されたが、いずれも軽傷だという。|現場は見通しのよい片側2車線の道路。|事故の原因は何だったのか。|警察によると、白い車は直進、黒い車は右折していて、その際に衝突したという。|また、白い車はレンタカーで、運転手は事故のあと、その場から立ち去っていた。|警察は、当時の信号の状況を調べるとともに、運転手の行方を追っている。|FNNプライムオンライン|https://www.fnn.jp/

title: Escaping Brazil's Deadliest Gangs
description: In the middle of the most violent regional capital in Brazil, a brutal gang war is being fought over control of the drug supply routes of the Northwestern Amazon region. Poverty and coercion force many young men into a life of crime where the only ways to escape are incarceration or death. |But amidst the carnage, there is a glimmer of hope - the “91” is a group of former gang lords turned pastors, who offer salvation to gang members who want to leave the criminal life. Their standing in the gang community, forged out of years of service and hard-fought respect, mean that only they can vouch for criminals looking to trade crime for the path of God.|By recording videos of these gangsters in repentance - that follow a tight script and are then shared with the higher ranks of the gangs for approval - they are saving hundreds of lives that Brazilian institutions overlook. title: SEHNSUCHT NACH WELTMACHT: Wanner - Darum will Putin die Ukraine unbedingt unterwerfen | WELT Analyse
description: Nach Einschätzung des britischen Generalstabschefs Tony Radakin hat Russland den Krieg gegen die Ukraine bereits jetzt "strategisch verloren". Der Angriff auf das Nachbarland sei ein "entsetzlicher Fehler Russlands" gewesen, sagte Radakin in einem am Freitag veröffentlichen Interview mit der Nachrichtenagentur Press Association (PA). Mit seinem Krieg gegen die Ukraine habe Russland die Nato gestärkt und Finnland und Schweden dazu gebracht, einen Aufnahmeantrag bei dem Militärbündnis zu stellen.|Es sei zwar möglich, dass Kreml-Chef Wladimir Putin in den kommenden Wochen "taktische Erfolge" in der Ukraine erzielen werde, sagte Radakin. Allerdings habe Putin ein Viertel der Stärke seiner Armee für "winzige" Geländegewinne geopfert. "Die russische Maschinerie wird zerrieben und sie gewinnt dabei täglich ein paar - zwei, drei, fünf - Kilometer." 50.000 russische Soldaten seien getötet oder verletzt worden. "Russland ist dabei zu scheitern."|Radakin sicherte der Ukraine die langfristige Unterstützung Großbritanniens im Kampf gegen die russischen Truppen zu. London liefere unter anderem Panzerabwehrwaffen an Kiew und werde dies weiter tun. |Moskau hatte den Westen am Donnerstag erneut vor der weiteren Unterstützung Kiews mit Waffen gewarnt. Dies sei "absolut nutzlos" und würden der Ukraine nur "weiter schaden", sagte Kreml-Sprecher Dmitri Peskow. |WELT Korrespondent Christoph Wanner schätzt diese Behauptung in Moskau ein.|#ukraine #russland #krieg|Der WELT Nachrichten-Livestream http://bit.ly/2fwuMPg|Abonniere den WELT YouTube Channel http://bit.ly/WeltVideoTVabo|Die Top-Nachrichten auf WELT.de http://bit.ly/2rQQD9Q|Unsere Reportagen & Dokumentationen http://bit.ly/WELTdokus|Die Mediathek auf WELT.de http://bit.ly/2Iydxv8|WELT Nachrichtensender auf Instagram https://bit.ly/IGWELTTV|WELT auf Instagram http://bit.ly/2X1M7Hk|In eigener Sache: Wegen des hohen Aufkommens unsachlicher und beleidigender Beiträge können wir zurzeit keine Kommentare mehr zulassen. |Danke für Eurer Verständnis - das WELT-Team|Video 2022 erstellt

title: Steigende Lebensmittelkosten - Rewe, Lidl und Co. im Vergleich | Marktcheck SWR
description: Ein Wocheneinkauf im Supermarkt oder Discounter reißt derzeit bei vielen ein Loch ins Portemonnaie. Warum ist das so? Wer profitiert davon? Und wo sind die Preise am niedrigsten?|----------- |Dieses Video ist eine Auskopplung aus der Sendung vom 14. Juni 2022. Ganze Marktcheck-Folgen inkl. Untertitel in der Mediathek: http://x.swr.de/s/13zv  |Bei diesem Film handelt es sich um eine Wiederholung aus der WDR-Markt-Sendung vom 01. Juni 2022.|----------- |PREISE STEIGEN|Im Vergleich zum Vorjahr sind Tomaten ca. 39 Prozent, Sonnenblumenöl 37 Prozent und Gurken 31 Prozent teurer. Auch aus diesem Grund gibt es mittlerweile viele Leute, die über Spendenaktionen der Tafel an Lebensmittel und Produkte kommen - darauf angewiesen sind. |WELCHER LADEN IST AM BESTEN?|Wir vergleichen die Preise von 35 Produkten, darunter Grundnahrungsmittel, Fleisch, Gemüse - aber auch einige Genussmittel wie Süßigkeiten, Bier und Sekt. Eingekauft haben wir bei Discountern und Supermärkten: Rewe, Edeka, Penny, Aldi, Netto und Lidl. Wir notieren dabei immer den billigsten Preis, wenn möglich pro Kilo oder pro Liter. In der Stichprobe: Einige Markenartikel, vor allem aber die günstigen No-Name-Produkte.|DAS ERGEBNIS|Das Ergebnis unserer Stichprobe: Bei Rewe war der Einkauf mit einem Gesamtpreis von 132,43 Euro am teuersten. Danach folgt Edeka, kaum günstiger mit 129,54 Euro, auf Platz fünf. Die Discounter sind günstiger. Platz vier Lidl, mit 123,60 Euro. Platz drei: Penny mit 120,17 Euro. Auf Platz zwei liegt Netto, denn hier gab es viele Sonderangebote, die den Gesamtpreis auf 119,90 Euro gesenkt haben. Unangefochten der billigste: Aldi mit 117,93 Euro.|Vor allem bei Obst und Gemüse sind Rewe und Edeka teurer als die Discounter. Preisunterschiede gab es auch bei den Markenprodukten. Bei Grundnahrungsmitteln liegen dagegen alle eng zusammen. Viele No-Name-Produkte kosten sogar bei allen gleich viel. Ein Kilo Zucker: 79 Cent. Ein Liter Milch: 92 Cent. Zehn Eier: 1,99 Euro. Selbst Salamipizza: Im Dreierpack 2,66 pro Kilo. Wer also konsequent nur Eigenmarken kauft, der kommt in allen Läden preislich ähnlich weg.|WESHALB STEIGEN DIE PREISE? |Im Zusammenhang mit Corona gibt es bereits seit zwei Jahren Preissteigerungen und der Ukraine-Krieg sorgte zuletzt für eine Verschärfung der Lage. Doch dies sind nicht die einzigen Gründe. Auch der schwache Euro trägt einen Teil zu den Preissteigerungen bei: Weil viele Waren auf dem Weltmarkt in Dollar bezahlt werden müssen, werden manche Lebensmittel noch teurer. Hinzu kommt, dass aktuell beispielsweise auch für Landwirte der Diesel teurer wird und die Transport- sowie Stromkosten steigen. Wenn viele Produzenten mit den Rücken zur Wand stehen, kann auch der Handel nicht mehr für günstige Preise sorgen. |----------- |Autorin: M. Fuchs, M. title: RUSIA cierra aún más el GRIFO del GAS a EUROPA y DISPARA su PRECIO | RTVE Noticias
description: El precio de la electricidad bajará con fuerza por el aumento de las renovables y un uso inferior del gas para generar electricidad. Sin embargo, el precio del gas aumenta. La razón: el cierre del grifo por parte de Rusia a Europa. Moscú ha reducido el volumen de gas que suministra al Viejo Continente a través del gaseoducto Nord Stream hasta los 67 millones de metros cúbicos diarios, lo que supone un 60% menos de su ritmo normal. |Desde la Comisión Europea aseguran que pese a ello, no habrá problemas de suministro. Sin embargo, sí que estamos viendo un aumento de los precios del gas pese al tope que estableció España. |#gas #electricidad #guerraucrania #rusia #preciogas #Putin  #precioluz #factura #luz #news #LiveNews #StreamingNews #españa #noticiasenespañol|👉👉 Más noticias: https://www.rtve.es/noticias|➤SUSCRÍBETE a RTVE Noticias en YouTube: https://bit.ly/2WtyvUx|✔️Síguenos en Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rtvenoticias/ |✔️Síguenos en Twitter: https://twitter.com/rtvenoticias|✔️Síguenos en Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RTVENoticias/

title: Top Channel/ ”Pikë kthese në historinë europiane”, Macron: Kujdes Ballkanin, reagon SHBA!
description: Kur gjëmimi i sirenave të alarmit tronditi qetësinë relative të Kievit mëngjesin e së enjtes, ishte një kujtesë e zymtë për presidentin Emmanuel Macron, kancelarin gjerman Olaf Scholz dhe kryeministrin Italian Mario Draghi se ai që po vizitonin, është në fakt një vend në luftë. Jo se ndiheshin të rrezikuar. |Sepse ashtu si liderë të tjerë përpara tyre, kujton CNN, drejt Ukrainës udhëtuan me një tren special që u nis nga Polonia në mes të natës dhe ruhej nga dhjetëra ushtarë të armatosur rëndë. Misioni i treshes së Kiev ishte të përpiqeshin të zbusnin tensionet mbi atë që qeveria ukrainase e perception si mungesë e një mbështetjeje të prekshme për të nga qeveritë e tyre. Shumë kritika kanë marrë javët e fundit sidomos Macron e Scholz, e presidenti ukrainas Volodymir Zelensky shkoi deri aty sa të sugjeronte se të dy ata po përpiqen ta marrin me te mirë Vladimir Putinin. |Por Macron dukej këtë radhë i vendosur ta ndryshonte një narrativë të tillë dhe në konferencën e përbashkët për shtyp pas takimit në kryeqytetin ukrainas, përcolli mbeshtetjen e shpresuar, ndërsa përmendi dhe Ballkanin. |Ne të gjithë jemi në favor që Ukrainës t'i jepet statusi i vendit kandidat për anëtarësim në Bashkimin Europian. Ky status do të shoqërohet me një  udhërrëfyes konkret dhe do të përfshijë marrjen parasysh edhe të situatës në Ballkanin Perëndimor. |Zelensky vetë e cilësoi takimin në Kiev si një hap shumë të madh përpara. |Kjo është një ditë historike. Ukraina ka ndjerë mbështetjen e katër shteteve të fuqishme europiane, që mbështesin rrugën tonë drejt BE-së: Italisë, Francës, Rumanisë dhe Gjermanisë, që të gjithë ata janë me ne. |Vendet lidere te bllokut europian treguan kështu solidaritet politik për kërkesën e Ukrainës për anëtarësim, e tani do të jetë samiti i BE-së që do të vendosë javën e ardhshme, nëse ajo do të marrë statusin e shumelakmuar të kandidatit. E enjtja duket ishte ditë offensive diplomatike në shumë plane për këtë vend. Shtetet e Bashkuara diskutuan me Kievin mundësinë e një zgjidhjeje të konfliktit me Rusinë përmes negociatave. |Megjithatë, këshilltari për sigurinë kombëtare në Shtëpinë e Bardhë, Jake Sullivan se theksoi se SHBA nuk do të bëjë presion ndaj Kievit për lëshime territoriale ndaj Rusisë. |Pamje: AFP|Departamenti i Informacionit, më i madhi, më kryesori në Top Channel, i cili shënoi fillimin e televizionit me edicionin e lajmeve në 20 dhjetor 2001. Përmes informacioneve të shpejta, të sakta dhe të thelluara, reportazheve dhe rubrikave të tjera informative, Top Channel është kthyer në burimin kryesor dhe me prestigjioz të informimit të të gjithëve në Shqipëri, në hapësirën mbarëshqiptare dhe kudo tjetër në botë ku shqiptarët jetojnë. Top Channel është i pranishëm me kamerat dhe gazetarët e tij në të gjitha ngjarjet më të rëndësishme të vendit dhe në botë, me edicionet e tij informative.|Për më shumë vizitoni: http://top-channel.tv/ |Subscribe to "Top Channel" on YouTube Channel for NEWS and TV |Shows HERE: http://bit.ly/2Y15KwK |For more content from click HERE: www.top-channel.tv |Like Top Channel on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/2FglWTs |Follow Top Channel on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/2uaYG2U |Follow Top Channel on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/2TJndeH |#Ukraine#BE#TopChannelNews

title: เปิดตัวเรือบรรทุกเครื่องบินจีนลำที่ 3 “สี จิ้นผิง”เตรียมหารือกลุ่ม BRICS | TNN ข่าวค่ำ | 17 มิ.ย. 65
description: กองทัพจีน เปิดตัวเรือบรรทุกเครื่องบินลำที่ 3 ชื่อ "ฝูเจี้ยน" ที่มีเทคโนโลยีคล้ายสหรัฐฯ ถือเป็นการเสริมสนยานุภาพทางทหาร ท่ามกลางสถานการณ์ความตึงเครียดด้านความมั่นคง ระหว่างสหรัฐฯ และไต้หวันทวีความรุนแรงขึ้น ด้าน ประธานาธิบดีสี จิ้นผิง เตรียมเข้าร่วมและเป็นประธานการประชุมสุดยอดผู้นำกลุ่มประเทศ “บริกส์” (BRICS) ซึ่ง ประกอบไปด้วยสมาชิก 5 ประเทศ ได้แก่ บราซิล, รัสเซีย, อินเดีย, จีน และแอฟริกาใต้ วันที่ 23 มิ.ย.นี้ ขณะที่ สหรัฐฯ ประกาศเดินหน้าความริเริ่มเพื่อกระชับความร่วมมือกับกลุ่มประเทศมหาสมุทรแปซิฟิก เพื่อคานอำนาจอิทธิพลของจีน|ช่องทางติดตามสถานีข่าว TNN ช่อง16|https://www.tnnthailand.com|https://tv.trueid.net/live/tnn16|https://www.youtube.com/c/tnn16|https://www.facebook.com/TNNthailand/|https://www.facebook.com/TNN16LIVE/|https://twitter.com/tnnthailand|https://www.instagram.com/tnn_online/|https://www.tiktok.com/@tnnonline|Line @TNNONLINE หรือคลิก https://lin.ee/4fP2tltIo|ทันโลก ทันเศรษฐกิจ ทันทุกความจริง กับ TNNช่อง16 สถานีข่าวที่ถือหลักการของการนำเสนอข่าวตรงประเด็น รวดเร็ว ถูกต้อง แม่นยำ และเป็นกลาง โดยทีมข่าวมืออาชีพ

title: “雲隠れ”吉川議員　町内会費未払いか「4万円のお小遣い払う金あるなら・・・」地元怒り(2022年6月17日)
description: 18歳の女性と飲酒したなどの疑惑で離党した吉川議員（40）が、いまだ雲隠れを続けています。地元関係者を取材すると、町内会費の不払いを巡ってトラブルになっていることが明らかになりました。|　雲隠れを続ける吉川議員。批判は17日もやみません。|　自民党富士市富士支部・稲葉寿利幹事長：「東京の夜の街で、このような事件を起こすことは言語道断であります」|　18歳の女性と飲酒したなどと報じられた吉川赳議員。|　支部から静岡県連へ、辞職勧告を求める上申書が出されました。|　これまで支えてきただけに怒りを隠せません。|　自民党富士市富士支部・前島貞一支部長：「今現状、姿を見せないことは非常識極まる。（連絡は）身内とも事務局とも全然取れていない。我々の所へ一つとしてわびの電話もありません。迷惑を掛けたなということもない。何を考えているのかなと」|　自民党・岸田派議員：「結果は明らかに見えてるのに、それに対する想像力があるかないかの話だよ。これだけ仲間に迷惑を掛けて、そんなことも分からないんじゃね」|　自民党関係者：「このまま放置して（参院）選挙戦にまで影響したら、岸田派への風当たりも強くなると思いますよ」|　議員宿舎周辺でも姿を見せず、雲隠れを続けています。|　クリーニング店：「うちのお客さん結構議員宿舎の人いるんですけど、吉川さんは見たことない」|　本人は色々と忙しいようです。|　自民党・岸田派議員：「自分で調べているらしいですよ。お店に電話したりしているらしい」|　18歳の女性と飲酒し、4万円のお小遣いをあげたとする週刊誌報道。地元の静岡では、“いい父親”ぶりを目撃されていました。|　吉川議員の自宅の近所の人：「下のお嬢さんと朝マックに行ったり、そんなことを聞いたことがあるので、忙しいのにと思っていた。子煩悩でいいお父さんだなと思っていますけどね」|　一方、実家の近くでは評判が一変します。|　2019年以前に住んでいたという家。ここで1カ月1500円の町内会費を払っていなかったそうです。拒否した理由は「近くに住む父親が払っている」。ただ、町内会費は一世帯ごとに払うルールです。|　実家の近所の人：「4万円のお小遣い払う金があるなら町内会費払えるだろうって話。一人暮らしの高齢者も払っているのに」|　そもそも、こんな評判もあります。|　実家の近所の人：「学生時代からいい話を聞かない。『うちの親父は議員だから』が口癖のような感じで、上から目線だったと聞いたことがある。あまり関わりたくない。けじめを付けてほしい」|[テレ朝ｎｅｗｓ] https://news.tv-asahi.co.jp
